                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370918-2103-offence-1 t18370918-cd-65"></join>15th of August</rs>, 1 glazier's diamond, value, 14<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18370918-name-445" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18370918-name-445" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
